" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d12c5ce28225b76326a61bc9dca9b28ee3159f","tid":971400,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T22:10:35.000Z","msg":"搞得周天寒徹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用毛魔詩詞，靚抽"},{"pid":"4e0d9c2d805430d0fefbb0593c782ecd075c8fa3","tid":971400,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f99cbe3051c27acb06da2347b1239ff5084d17fd","tid":971400,"uid":66242,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"侵曾經直接同中国人喺貿易上交過手<br />\n應該無其他美國總統有佢呢個親身閱歷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T00:30:43.000Z","msg":"所以先無d左膠咁on9仲信支國人<br />\n明明違反左咁多承諾仲俾機會佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}